The paper discusses formal verification of algorithms for differential privacy, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper also introduces a new language and type system for this purpose, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The use of dependent types and inference engine also suggests a connection to database theory (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE).
